==[[Final Fantasy V enemy AI|AI script]]==
<pre style="white-space: pre; overflow-x: auto; max-width: 100%;">
ACTIVE RULES:
  Default rule:
    Conditions:
      Unconditional
    Actions:
      Turn #1: random(!Attack, !Attack, Special: Yagyuu's Strike)
REACTIVE RULES:
  Rule #1:
    Conditions:
      Just before dying
      Lone enemy (duplicates do not count as separate enemies)
    Actions:
      Prepare to show/hide enemies:
        Enemy slots with shown enemies: [#2]
        Behaviour:
          - Do not transfer HP to the newly shown enemy/enemies
          - Show all enemies from the specified slots
          - Style: Discreet
      Ability: [Unhide enemy]
  Rule #2:
    Conditions:
      Just before dying
    Actions:
      Prepare to show/hide enemies:
        Enemy slots with shown enemies: [#2, #3]
        Behaviour:
          - Do not transfer HP to the newly shown enemy/enemies
          - Show all enemies from the specified slots
          - Style: Discreet
      Ability: [Unhide enemy]
  Rule #3:
    Conditions:
      Hit by !Attack
    Actions:
      random(Image, [Nothing], [Nothing])
</pre>
